    <div class="card my-3" style="width: 100%; padding: 30px">
      <div class="card-body" >
        <h3 class="card-title">What is CommandConsole?</h3>
        <p class="class-text">
            CommandConsole is a fast, secure and lightweight shell which can
          automate tasks for you. It takes care of the user and has a
          user-freindly interface.<br />
          It is a cross-platform application which can be used in windows, linux
          and macOS. It is open-source and anybody can contribute in it.<br />
         
        </p>
        <br>
        <h3 class="card-title">Features</h3>
        <p class="card-text">
            <ol>
                <li><code>help</code> system included </li>
                <li>user-freindly interactive interface</li>
                <li>password management</li>
                <li>command line history</li>
                <li>command line editor</li>
                <li>automation of tasks</li>
                <li>Ease update</li>
            </ol>

        </p>
        <br>
        <h3 class="card-title">Configuration of CommandConsole</h3>
        <p class="card-text">
            CommandConsole is written in <b>C language</b>. All the comands which are being used in CommandConsole are the function statements. <br>
            The functions are written in <code>.h</code> header file - <code>MainCommands.h</code>. And the main program of executing these commands are written in<br>
            <code>Main.c</code> file. To update, we have included <code>update.sh</code>. 
            <br><br>
            (ðŸ˜œ Do not need to worry. You did not have to download any thing like - mingw, or any code file. <br>We will provide an <code>.exe</code> file in which the main application is there.)
        </p>
